:{"pid":"cb73d7d578aa4726aaf1a992c36b057790e08a57","tid":2214181,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"大把司機都車住桶油渣周圍走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"啲吊車司機個個都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c8e10482df8e6c7646ea6a570e087b8ea4db8","tid":2214181,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"上訴庭繼續表演守尾門角色<br />\n只要咩案都推到上訴庭<br />\n搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d78848b82e0ba17a8cd223edbb7ee51e5e581b","tid":2214181,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，<del>好大機會</del><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong>包括</strong></ins></span><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ac7ada7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"fc6cdc1b7c5dc77623c3e4edf27fa19492d4e75e","tid":2214181,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049c8e10482df8e6c7646ea6a570e087b8ea4db8","tid":2214181,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"上訴庭繼續表演守尾門角色<br />\n只要咩案都推到上訴庭<br />\n搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:55:28.000Z","msg":"有潘書記唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}